Package: REBET
Title: The subREgion-based BurdEn Test (REBET)
Version: 1.4.0
Date: 2018-08-13
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        "Bill", "Wheeler", email = "wheelerb@imsweb.com", role=c("cre")
