Description: There is an increasing focus to investigate the association between rare variants
 and diseases. The REBET package implements the subREgion-based BurdEn Test which is a
 powerful burden test that simultaneously identifies susceptibility loci and sub-regions.
Imports: stats, utils
Depends: ASSET
